Pit your wits against other players in the exciting game that used to be played by royalty in ancient India. Place your fate on the roll of the dice, decide your strategy and move your tokens to reach the centre. What makes Ludo so addictive is its simplicity. Between mastering the game and trying to beat other players, you can sink into the game for hours without realising it.

